            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>02.</strong> Strong standards alignment and assessment mapping in a regulated educational context.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>03.</strong> Clear translation of complex technical content into age-appropriate instructional language.</li>
            <li class="list-group-item"><strong>04.</strong> Effective collaboration with clients and developers while protecting instructional intent.</li>
